AUDIO: 'So, I recently did a video where I talked about DistroKid. So, I thought that I\'d quickly cover it in this video. So, in terms of releasing my AI music, DistroKid is definitely number one in my opinion.'

[00:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'It\'s been the easiest way for me to get AI music onto distribution platforms such as Spotify, Apple Music, etc. Spotify is generally there within 24 hours.'

[00:27] [scene:talk]
