AUDIO: 'And you can also add your releases to TikTok and many different other platforms as you can see here. Apple Music, iTunes, Apple. You\'ve got Spotify, Pandora. There\'s so many to select, which is great. Now, in terms of'

[00:41] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'what DistroKid costs, you do pay for subscription, but the benefit is you keep 100% of your earnings. Now, I\'ve used many different distribution platforms for the last 20 years at'

[00:55] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'least. And I\'m finding that DistroKid, even though there is a monthly service, the service is brilliant. The support team are excellent. And as I say, in terms of releasing your'

[01:07] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'general music, but especially if you\'re releasing AI music, I would suggest DistroKid. Now, there is a caveat. And the caveat is that DistroKid is up for sale.'

[01:20] [scene:talk]
