AUDIO: 'So, if you\'re really worried about that in terms of changes, then you may not want to go ahead. Now, in terms of how much it costs, you\'ve got the musician plus, which is $3.75 a month or billed annually at $45. That'

[01:32] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'gives you two artists, and that\'s what I\'m currently with at the moment. Because I\'ve got a couple of AI artists in the worst works as well as my own music. So, I felt that that was really good. You\'ve'

[01:46] [scene:talk]
